summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of that portion of the south 96 feet of the north 396 feet of the northeast quarter of the northeast quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W. M., with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-403 and 17-297, respectively.
